reviewText: Love his series. Very thought provoking and informative.
A Nother great video from Chuck his ministry thanks for the word
I did not see that it was not the whole set. But has a lot of info on the book of Revelation.
Very interesting and indepth series on the book of revelation.

One of the most complete commentaries on Revelation you will find anywhere. As always, Chuck Missler
has an amazing grasp of his subject matter and mines out many nuggets buried in God's word.
Excellent material! I recommend it to anyone who wants to dive into the Book of Revelation.

Made 2006, Futurist, Literal, Rapture Pre-Tribulational, Premillennial, well researched, Scripture interprets Scripture, recommend Comprehensive Workbook.  Unfortunately, 4 DVD's scratched with 1 unable to read,  seller provided phone number and kindly refunded.

This product and Amazon costumer service were both great. I would highly recommend this product. Reasonably prices . Will Buy from Again. I love just about everything from Mr. Missler. A very wise and trusting man. We can learn a lot from his wisdom on our BIBLE.Thank You
